      "span_text": "with 10% FBS. Primary cultures of HUVEC were established by isolating ECs from umbilical cords with collagenase digestion, as described.  Primary EC cultures from eight separate donors were used for this study. Adult Human Dermal Microvascular Endothelial cells (HMVECs)"
